In the INTEREST OF A.S.-M. and A.C., Minor Children, C.C., Father of A.C., Appellant, K.S.-M., Mother, Appellant. No. 18-1905 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother appeals the termination of her parental rights to two children. The father of one of the children appeals the termination of his parental rights. AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.

AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.
